{"tid":409243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鄰國送大禮] 標普下調香港評級至AA+ 展望穩定","createTime":"2017-09-22T02:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T02:04:54.000Z","uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdeb8a01db89801e6507ca1ce32466a815f0ffe1","tid":409243,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:02:51.000Z","msg":"評級機構標普下調香港長期評級，由「AAA」調低至「AA+」，前景展望穩定。<br />\n<br />\n標普表示，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港與內地有很強關係性，是次調低評級是因為已將內地評級下調</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n標普昨日下調中國主權信用評級，長期主權信用評級由「AA-」下調至「A+」；短期主權信用評級由「A-1+」下調至「A-1」，長期評級展望為穩定。"},{"pid":"a14ce0025f412e2c6f958826c784850ba161304b","tid":409243,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"913017561040b3b73b53493e67bdb84ce876192a","tid":409243,"uid":139704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"共享繁榮安定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}